@startuml sequence_math_operation

participant "Actor" as Actor
participant "Calculator" as Calc
participant "math" as Math

== Happy Path: square_root(16) ==

Actor ->> Calc : square_root(16)
activate Calc
note right of Calc : x=16, domain check: 16 >= 0, passes
Calc ->> Math : sqrt(16)
activate Math
Math --> Calc : 4.0
deactivate Math
Calc --> Actor : 4.0
deactivate Calc

== Error Path: natural_log(-5) ==

Actor ->> Calc : natural_log(-5)
activate Calc
note right of Calc : x=-5, domain check: -5 <= 0, fails
Calc --> Actor : raise ValueError
deactivate Calc

@enduml
